What if someone sees us?

00:00:15,473 --> 00:00:17,342
Please, this place is
like a ghost town.

00:00:17,342 --> 00:00:19,177
Well, what about God?

00:00:19,177 --> 00:00:21,212
He sees everything.

00:00:21,212 --> 00:00:23,581
Well, I mean, if he
has a problem with it,

00:00:23,581 --> 00:00:26,050
he'll let us know,
right?

00:00:51,142 --> 00:00:52,977
Uh, you're, um...
What?

00:00:52,977 --> 00:00:54,145
There's, uh...

00:00:54,145 --> 00:00:56,214
You're covered in...
(screams)

00:00:56,214 --> 00:00:57,482
(siren wails)

00:00:57,482 --> 00:00:59,450
Is it really...?

00:00:59,450 --> 00:01:01,219
Blood?

00:01:01,219 --> 00:01:03,354
Yeah.

00:01:03,354 --> 00:01:04,489
(indistinct radio transmission)

00:01:04,489 --> 00:01:06,024
Excuse me.

00:01:11,963 --> 00:01:15,466
So, I talked
to Kid Casanova.

00:01:15,466 --> 00:01:18,369
He tells me that God's
wrath rained down.

00:01:18,369 --> 00:01:20,905
You know, you lose the blood
and the police tape,

00:01:20,905 --> 00:01:22,440
my wife could
really go

00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:24,942
for a neighborhood
like this.

00:01:24,942 --> 00:01:28,346
Very eco-friendly.

00:01:28,346 --> 00:01:30,281
WILLOWS:
Not so friendly tonight.

00:01:30,281 --> 00:01:33,017
The Chambliss family.
Quadruple homicide.

00:01:33,017 --> 00:01:35,286
You're gonna need backup.

00:01:35,286 --> 00:01:37,388
You get many "Stigmata"
houses in Seattle?

00:01:37,388 --> 00:01:40,258
No, no, our saints bleed coffee
up there.

00:01:40,258 --> 00:01:42,126
BRASS: The owner was a
pharmaceutical salesman.

00:01:42,126 --> 00:01:43,261
Laid off six months ago.

00:01:43,261 --> 00:01:45,463
Okay, thank you.
I got it.

00:01:47,231 --> 00:01:50,234
Well, I hope Moonbeam
brought his booties

00:01:50,234 --> 00:01:51,869
and a strong stomach.

00:01:53,905 --> 00:01:55,106
(sighs)

00:01:55,106 --> 00:01:56,340
(door creaks)

00:02:21,899 --> 00:02:26,270
(indistinct sportscast
plays on TV)

00:02:32,410 --> 00:02:35,213
ANNOUNCER: ...retain possession,
very, very lucky.

00:02:35,213 --> 00:02:37,181
Lining up for the next play, Al.

00:02:37,181 --> 00:02:40,418
That'll make it second down and
a loss of five on the play.

00:02:40,418 --> 00:02:42,987
Second down and 15...

00:02:47,058 --> 00:02:49,360
(whirring)

00:03:17,288 --> 00:03:19,223
Greenhouse
gray water system.

00:03:19,223 --> 00:03:22,827
Recycles everything that goes
down the drain.

00:03:22,827 --> 00:03:24,295
And out to
the sprinklers.

00:03:24,295 --> 00:03:26,330
Explains why
the house was bleeding.

00:03:32,036 --> 00:03:33,905
Look at this.

00:03:33,905 --> 00:03:38,042
When was the last time you
bought a rainbow marshmallow?

00:03:38,042 --> 00:03:39,877
When my daughter was eight.

00:03:39,877 --> 00:03:41,445
Oh, God.

00:03:48,386 --> 00:03:49,954
Do you feel that?

00:03:49,954 --> 00:03:52,190
Change in temperature.

00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:54,425
(door creaks)

00:04:14,378 --> 00:04:15,479
RUSSELL:
Oh.

00:04:18,149 --> 00:04:21,385
There's no blood on
her pajamas.

00:04:21,385 --> 00:04:23,087
She's been redressed.

00:04:23,087 --> 00:04:25,189
Cleaned up,
tucked in.

00:04:26,991 --> 00:04:28,826
By somebody
who cared about her.

00:04:38,436 --> 00:04:41,372
This was where she was shot.

00:04:47,545 --> 00:04:49,213
What's blood doing way up there?

00:05:18,209 --> 00:05:19,477
(indistinct radio transmission)

00:05:25,516 --> 00:05:28,886
Wait here till
you get the Code Four.

00:05:30,554 --> 00:05:32,490
(door creaks)

00:05:38,095 --> 00:05:40,331
OFFICER: Got someone over here.
Show me your hands!

00:05:40,331 --> 00:05:43,134
Get down on your knees!
Get down on your knees!

00:05:43,134 --> 00:05:45,436
Sounds like a Code Four to me.

00:05:45,436 --> 00:05:48,306
BRASS: Let me see your hands!
Get down on the ground!
Get down on the ground!

00:05:48,306 --> 00:05:50,241
Let me see those hands!
Get him down!

00:05:50,241 --> 00:05:52,376
Get him on the ground!
Get on the ground!
I loved her!

00:05:52,376 --> 00:05:55,546
Do not resist!
Cuff him up.

00:05:55,546 --> 00:05:59,016
I loved her! Oh, God!

00:05:59,016 --> 00:06:01,085
Cuff him.
Get him out of here!

